      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is used under a validated installation with documented regression test suite. Version control and change-log review required.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is deployed under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. Installation qualification records, regression test suite results (847 benchmark cases), and software change log reviewed and approved by the modeling team quality assurance officer. Achieved level exceeds required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
